platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: Let the rhythm fill your soul

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 撞擊圖騰雕像，㪣響解謎韻律

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: This chilled-out title has a rhythm all of its own. By dropping tiny spirits into place, you’re not just solving the puzzle – you’re adding beats to the jam. Sit back, pop on your headphones and enjoy the relaxed grooves as you work your way through some delightfully animated levels.
